<div class="container">
        <h2>Need <span id="meal">lunch</span> for <span id="number">80</span> on <span id="day">Friday</span>? Done.</h2>
        
        <div class="placard alpha">
                <h1>a simple 3 step guide to creating an event</h1>

            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step1">
                    <h2>Tell us about your event</h2>
                   <%= image_tag "organizers/organizers-tellus.png", class:"organizers-steps image-alpha" %>
                   <%= image_tag "organizers/organizers-arrow.png", class:"organizers-arrow" %>
                   <p>Fill out the form below will as much detail as you know so that we are fully informed on what you need.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step2">
                    <h2>We'll collect bids</h2>
                    <%= image_tag "organizers/organizers-bids.png", class:"organizers-steps image-alpha" %>
                    <%= image_tag "organizers/organizers-arrow.png", class:"organizers-arrow" %>
                    <p>Restaurants are dying to host your event. We’ll make sure you get the best deal possible.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step3">
                    <h2>Pick a vendor</h2>
                    <%= image_tag "organizers/organizers-vendor.png", class:"organizers-steps" %>
                    <p>You’ll get to choose from a couple of different options. Pick a vendor and pay them directly.</p>
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="placard beta">
          <%= image_tag "stringleft.png", class:"stringleft" %>
          <%= image_tag "stringright.png", class:"stringright" %>

          <h1>what you need to know</h1>
          <div id="needtoknow">
          <p><strong>Complete this form to receive bids from several restaurants for your event.</strong> Our priority is to curate "safe bets" -- options highly likely to succeed based on your preferences. For every person ordered for, one meal will be given to a child in need, locally or abroad. (Buy One, Feed One.)</p><br />
          <p>We work quick, with bids returned within 24hrs. However, please give notice well in advance for restaurants, when possible.<br /><strong>Thanks for using our service for your event.</strong></p>
          </div>     
        </div>

        <div class="placard omega">
          <%= image_tag "stringleft.png", class:"stringleft" %>
          <%= image_tag "stringright.png", class:"stringright" %>

            <h1>Sign up</h1>
            <%= form_tag organizers_path, :id => "organizers", method: :post do %>
                <h2>Will this be for dine-in or dine-out?</h2>
                <%= radio_button_tag :location, 'at the restaurant', value: "1", class: "custom-input" %>
                <%= label_tag 'at the restaurant', 'Dining at Restaurant' %>
                <br />
                <%= radio_button_tag :location, 'different location', value: "2", class: "custom-input" %>
                <%= label_tag 'different location', 'Dining at a different location' %>
                <br />
                <%= text_field_tag :address, nil, placeholder: "Delivery address", size: "60", class: 'field standart organizers-field' %>
                <h2>What date and time will this event be?</h2>
                <%= text_field_tag :date, nil, size: "60", class: 'field standart organizers-field' %>
                <h2>How many people would you like to order food for?</h2>
                <%= text_field_tag :num_people, nil, size: "60", class: 'field standart organizers-field' %>
                <h2>Is there an occassion? (i.e. family party, work celebration, etc)</h2>
                <%= text_field_tag :occassion, nil, size: "60", class: 'field standart organizers-field' %>
                <h2>What is the specified budget</h2>
                <p>add a desired per head or total cost here</p>
                <%= text_field_tag :budget, nil, size: "60", class: 'field standart organizers-field' %>
                <h2>We will send you some great recommendations, but are there any preferences right off-the-bat?</h2>
                <p>(food types, spicy/non-spicy, allergies, etc.)</p>
                <%= text_field_tag :food_preferences, nil, size: "60", class: 'field standart organizers-field' %>
                <h2>Who is the ringleader?</h2>
                <p>Please enter a valid email address for us to follow up with.</p>
                <%= text_field_tag :email, nil, size: "60", class: 'field standart organizers-field' %>
                <h2>To Where Should We Donate Meals?</h2>
                <%= radio_button_tag :donation, 'locally', value: 'locally', class: "custom-input", id: 'donation_locally', checked: 'checked' %>
                <%= label_tag 'locally', 'Locally - <a href="www.kidsfoodbasket.org">www.kidsfoodbasket.org</a>'.html_safe, for: 'donation_locally' %>
                <br />
                <%= radio_button_tag :donation, 'globally', value: 'globally', class: "custom-input"%>
                <%= label_tag 'globally', 'Globally - <a href="www.worldvision.org">www.worldvision.org</a>'.html_safe, for: 'donation_globally' %>
                <br />
                <h2>Bear with us as we grow. Is there any feedback you have about this form or about this process?</h2>
                <%= text_area_tag :feedback, nil, rows: "10", cols: "60", class: 'field standart organizers-field' %><br />
                <%= submit_tag "Submit", :class => "btn-standart" %>
            <% end %>
            </div>
        </div>

<script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.8.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
